				<div class="hvres-meaning">Âm Pinyin: <a href="/py/bian1">biān <span class="small gray han">ㄅㄧㄢ</span></a><br>Âm Nôm: <a href="/nom/bàm">bàm</a>, <a href="/nom/bẳm">bẳm</a>, <a href="/nom/biêm">biêm</a>, <a href="/nom/biìm">biìm</a>, <a href="/nom/bìm">bìm</a>, <a href="/nom/bơm">bơm</a><br>Âm Nhật (onyomi): <a href="/reading/1/1/ヘン">ヘン (hen)</a><br>Âm Nhật (kunyomi): <a href="/reading/1/2/いしばり">いしばり (ishibari)</a><br>Âm Hàn: <a href="/reading/1/3/폄">폄</a><br>Âm Quảng Đông: <a href="/reading/1/4/bin1">bin1</a></div><p class="hvres-source">Tự hình <span class="badge">2</span></p>
